This is my new (first) Mini Game map

What do you have to do?

well this is a trampolin arena you get boosted into air when hitting trampolin 

Each team gets color so its easyer T: red CT: blue (ofc)

Now your mission: To kill the other team with either Knife, Elites (hard) or M3

Dont camp @spawn you will get killed after 15 sec...
